<h2 class="title"><a href="/blog/luisnassif/arthur-virgilio-e-as-farc">Arthur Virgilio e as FARC</a></h2>
    <span class="submitted">Enviado por luisnassif, ter, 20/07/2010 - 09:11</span>
    <!--<div class="taxonomy"><ul class="links inline"><li class="taxonomy_term_944 first"><a href="/categoria/tags-do-blog/arthur-virgilio" rel="tag" title="">Arthur Virgílio</a></li>
